title: The Vlog Squad Responds - H3 After Dark #26
description: On this episode of H3 After Dark Ethan & Hila address Scott Sire's PR video running interference for David. Later in the episode we have some goofs and light hearted gaffs talking about crazy Christian TikTok, R Kelly, and a whole lot more!
